<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <div  style="margin: 0 auto; width: 50%;">
    <title>Techmenu Chatbot</title>
    </div>
    <style>
       <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="static/style.css">
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div  style="margin: 0 auto; width: 50%;">
    <h1>Wiki Chatbot</h1>
    <p>Hi, I am Wiki Chatbot. As ChatGPT does not have access to current news or events beyond its knowledge cutoff of September 2021, I am here to help.</p>
    <p>The information after September 2021 was trained with OpenAI LLM with Llama_Index library.</p>
    <p>For example, you can ask me questions like:</p>
    <p><i>Why was Mr Trump indicted, who is Stormy Danniels, who is Michael Cohen </p></i>
    <p><i>Tell me the scandle between trump and stormy daniels, etc </p></i>
    <p></p>
    <p><b>Be aware, I am using a free tier API key which is heavily rate-limited by OpenAI so the response may take 30 - 60 seconds, please be patient.</p></b>
    
    <div id="chatbox"></div>
    <form id="user-input" style="width: 2500px; height: 300px;">
        <label for="name">You: </label>
        <input type="text" name="user_message"><br><br>
    </form>
    <script src="static/chatbot.js"></script>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
